                    <MudIconButton Href="https://github.com/ChristianHinkle/CppUtils" Target="_blank" Size="@Size.Small" Icon="@MBELIcons.Material.LinkClassicSolid"></MudIconButton><span class="ch-resume-item-category-text">CppUtils - </span>Wrote a collection of general purpose C++ libraries with no external dependencies.
